%F A104272 a(n) = prime(2n) + A233739(n) = (A233822(n) + a(n+1))/2. - _Jonathan Sondow_, Dec 16 2013
%F A104272 a(n) = max{prime p: pi(p) - pi(p/2) = n} (see Shevelev 2012). - _Jonathan Sondow_, Mar 23 2016
